_sText:
This is a small map I'm creating for my clan server, its more or less to just get back into the good old mapping habit since I haven't released a map in ages. I figured instead of an ordinary dev map I'd use the hardly used dev textures. :P

I wanted to just release a MiP instead of a beta map, sorry for posting it so late, I was expecting this to be a 2 hr job, but its carried on much longer than that.

Please give me some feedback , it's based more around fun than anything, so please take that more into mind.

ATM I need to add a secret egg (or multiple) fix up a few brushes I don't like, possibly make a room ontop of spawn, make an obvious party room (where you won't be able to kill people but after a minute it'll blow up so rounds aren't delayed too much) and a few other things to increase overall gameplay and whatnot.

I'll likely add some tunnels going underground / onto the side of the map.
